<br>
As for your info, that about explains what I believe. But keep in mind that I am a solitary practitioner. I do not belong to a coven. My spirituality is personal and kept on a personal basis. I find no reason to have a &quot;middle man&quot; concerning my relationship with my Goddess.  <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:purple;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Mysidia Drakkenbane</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END-->: 51 Human Druid<br>
